## Component Priority (from PRD)

### P0 - Must Have (Build First)
- Layout, Header, Footer
- HeroMain
- FeatureGrid
- PricingTable
- CTASection
- ContactForm (React island)

### P1 - Should Have
- HeroSimple
- FeatureShowcase
- Testimonial
- LogoCloud
- BlogCard, BlogPost
- CostCalculator (React island)

### P2 - Nice to Have
- TestimonialCarousel
- StatsBar
- ProductDemo
- VideoPlayer
- AuthorCard

## Content Collections

```typescript
// src/content/config.ts
import { defineCollection, z } from 'astro:content';

const blog = defineCollection({
  type: 'content',
  schema: z.object({
    title: z.string(),
    description: z.string(),
    pubDate: z.date(),
    updatedDate: z.date().optional(),
    author: z.string().default('beings-team'),
    category: z.string(),
    tags: z.array(z.string()),
    image: z.string().optional(),
  }),
});

export const collections = { blog };
```

## Page Templates

Each page should:
1. Import Layout component
2. Define SEO metadata in frontmatter
3. Compose from marketing components
4. Use semantic HTML structure

```astro
---
import Layout from '../components/layout/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/marketing/Hero.astro';
import FeatureGrid from '../components/marketing/FeatureGrid.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/marketing/CTASection.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Beings - Qualitative Research Platform',
  description: 'AI-powered qualitative coding for researchers',
};
---

<Layout {...seo}>
  <Hero />
  <FeatureGrid />
  <CTASection />
</Layout>
```

## Deployment

- **Platform:** Cloudflare Pages
- **Build:** `npm run build` в†’ `dist/`
- **Preview:** Automatic on PR
- **Production:** Auto-deploy on main branch
